  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project consists of training my young children in rural areas on their rights and their duties, explaining the content of the Sustainable Development Goal 4 (SDG4) with examples leading them to be implemented in their current practices. This project will also inspire target groups to stop all forms of violation of children&apos;s rights as well as inhuman treatment against girls and women because, in the implementation, it will be about strengthening the capacities of the groups.</narrative>
